{"id": 1625, "genre": 1001, "title": "这年头，你领教过哪些变相“通货膨胀”？", "description": "要么是价钱不变体验下降，要么是压根没便宜的可选，心塞。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 4878, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170412152557EI9ekDaCiuYW1fgR.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-14T03:00:46Z", "options": [{"id": 192513, "content": "同样的价格，送的快餐分量越来越少，口味越来越差。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937443}, {"id": 192514, "content": "随便一个xx包加一杯咖啡或啥的，起码60打底，要知道在学校在可能就七块钱的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273397}, {"id": 192516, "content": "以前一百可以花一个星期，现在只能用一上午。。，", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004753}, {"id": 192772, "content": "115会员", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881241}, {"id": 192520, "content": "鸡蛋灌饼越来越贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250675}, {"id": 194312, "content": "不知道赚多少钱才能过富足的老年生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009185}, {"id": 192521, "content": "羊肉泡馍没三十拿不下来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 856365}, {"id": 194569, "content": "养老金不断的加，物价不断的升", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009896}, {"id": 193547, "content": "吃个外卖五十块！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006158}, {"id": 192524, "content": "陌陌双曲线我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871531}, {"id": 193292, "content": "以前一百万可以买个house,现在可以买个厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006915}, {"id": 192525, "content": "语言通货膨胀。满地女神男神老戏骨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928245}, {"id": 192781, "content": "高中时老师告诉我们大学的饭菜很便宜，两块钱就能吃饱，现在我大一了，小份的面就要6块钱，一天光吃饭就要二十多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916686}, {"id": 192526, "content": "发工资的时候钱包没鼓起来，别人也看不出来你发工资了。就这样一句话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948083}, {"id": 193295, "content": "房价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006926}, {"id": 192528, "content": "我真的后悔结婚了 我看不到我的未来 我感觉我就是一个可悲的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004803}, {"id": 192529, "content": "前两年15元豪华午餐能吃饱，现在15元汉堡就手掌大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136326}, {"id": 192785, "content": "每次菜价上升，学校的伙食费涨价，从未降价过！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184301}, {"id": 192530, "content": "以前快车几块钱到处走，还都是现在专车的车型。现在快车能坐到一辆八万以上是运气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136326}, {"id": 192531, "content": "一杯喜茶，动辄二三十，排队三小时，喝完五分钟…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 644868}, {"id": 192532, "content": "羽绒服过去150元可以买接近顶级的品质，现在1500元才买到一件刚刚达到满意标准的羽绒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961241}, {"id": 192534, "content": "我只想说，兰州的是  兰州牛肉面，不是兰州拉面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964010}, {"id": 192535, "content": "门口的椰子从两三块钱涨到八块 感觉我一个土著都吃不起椰子了 心很痛 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 389468}, {"id": 192538, "content": "麦当劳吉士蛋汉堡的面包换成硬的了，贼难吃，还说是升级，简直想骂人", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919181}, {"id": 193308, "content": "巨无霸减肥了，我却越来越胖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792814}, {"id": 194846, "content": "小时候吃的五毛钱的东西现在换了包装，变成了十多块钱，，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010345}, {"id": 193825, "content": "总结就是  花的钱越来越多 得到东西越来越少", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008054}, {"id": 192547, "content": "早上的热干面碗越来越小", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920921}, {"id": 193827, "content": "满多少送多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950510}, {"id": 192548, "content": "没有，反正卡里一直是余额状态。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004867}, {"id": 193319, "content": "以前，坐公交车都是两毛钱，现在起步价两元钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006975}, {"id": 194087, "content": "变了  真的变了   曾经和现在已经有距离了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259948}, {"id": 192552, "content": "之前早餐三块钱，现在十几块钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937748}, {"id": 192553, "content": "以前100块钱可以用很久，现在100块钱跟以前10块钱一样，吃两顿快餐没了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004889}, {"id": 193322, "content": "究竟是我手长大了还是包子变小了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159149}, {"id": 192555, "content": "以前一杯奶茶几块钱，现在都二十几块了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999926}, {"id": 192558, "content": "价格不变，包装变小", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881438}, {"id": 192560, "content": "我没感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998737}, {"id": 193072, "content": "商场很少进，基本上都在X宝上买，其实还是比较喜欢过去逛商场买衣服的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006363}, {"id": 192561, "content": "摊煎饼都要10块钱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531129}, {"id": 193073, "content": "看看快餐店汉堡的大小吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972661}, {"id": 192563, "content": "以前是可以生活。现在是活着生存", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995866}, {"id": 192564, "content": "1块钱的馒头越来越小了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004913}, {"id": 192565, "content": "以前拿出一百块买东西时，内心盛满了土豪感，现在拿出一百块满心等待找钱，却看到收银员满脸的不够钱，内心顿时塞满土鳖感", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004082}, {"id": 194101, "content": "闪存的起始容量越来越大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008754}, {"id": 192823, "content": "以前没钱买华为，现在没钱买华为", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931864}, {"id": 192824, "content": "学校的网费还是那么多 然而网速越来越慢  网络越来越卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290302}, {"id": 193080, "content": "我就说德克士这家快餐店吧，到了晚上顾客以前的时候，我怀疑他们都在买库存的食物，经常点餐的时候，有些东西都没有，逼着你要选择他们给你提供的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006384}, {"id": 192569, "content": "滴滴 滴滴 滴滴 \n这车费像打劫一样?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660406}, {"id": 199738, "content": "买菜的时候，菜农再也不会送我葱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 497893}]}